Summary: white light moving high up and moved steadily vanishing as it went
divs: Sighting DetailsOn monday evening about 815pm i was walking to the car outside my home with two other people. It was beginning to be nighttime and we looked up in the sky and and saw a plane and then a white object moving steadily across the sky. no color lights...moving towards tucson. and within minutes the object blinked out of sight. It was no longer there and the other plane in the sky kept flying by it was still going across the sky while the other one had blinked out already gone.
